effect too.  I mean there are not that many places to solo 50+ in the Old World, while on Kunark and Velious there are tons, and you can med w/ the extra mana to solo more.  Please could people post their views and help me out in this decision b/c although I am not 50 yet I will be getting my epic pretty soon and would like to know other's views on this topic.  Thanks <p><p><font size="2"><b><font color="#FF1100">Fendien Elliminster<BR>
